dct_title_s: Working Plan for S.E. Quarter. F.L. & J.C. Olmsted, Landscape Architects
dct_description_sm: Oversize; Showing 1/4 of main quad, with seemingly partially complete inner quad, and south half of east lateral quad (“to be used for Boys’ playground until required for building purposes”), area behind main quad (“this to be reserved for workshops”), street & lot subdivision, botanical garden.
